overview:
Concepted in 2011 after I left 10 year career in Law Enforcement

Design is intended to be the most useful, logical and user friendly social group ever

Stuff you can do is classified for now, but imagine every tool you ever wanted available to make you as much money as desired

As well we intend to work with any other social networks, etc. if they desire.

Currently working on a smartphone integration, special addons, and looking for a serious investor of at least 1 million dollars.
